PN,41401
SC,0001
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F414A1774631480
OL,3,CWoman who had upto 300 seizures before
OL,4,Cbreakfast hails life-changing treatment
OL,6,FA woman from Buckinghamshire who
OL,7,Fsuffered up to 300 seizures before
OL,8,Fbreakfast has described the impact of
OL,9,Fundergoing "life-changing" treatment.
OL,11,FHolly Edwards, 29, from Haddenham
OL,12,Fsuffers from drug-resistant epilepsy
OL,13,Fand said it has left her facing long
OL,14,Fperiods of isolation.
OL,16,FAt worst Holly can experience up to
OL,17,F300 seizures before 9am, and only one
OL,18,Fin around 100 people in the UK have
OL,19,Fthe condition.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G1/9
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
