OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,415,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41402
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F414A1774631480
OL,3,CWoman who had upto 300 seizures before
OL,4,Cbreakfast hails life-changing treatment
OL,6,FOn International Epilepsy Day - Holly
OL,7,Fwants to raise awareness of the daily
OL,8,Fphysical struggles and the mental toll
OL,9,F- it takes.
OL,11,F"I think one of the difficult things
OL,12,Fthat people don't notice is you sort
OL,13,Fof get up and try, but it's like
OL,14,Fwalking through tar in the morning,"
OL,15,FHolly said.
OL,17,F"I wake up at around 6.40, I'm having
OL,18,Fseizures, and I can barely brush my
OL,19,Fteeth.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G2/9
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,415,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41403
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F414A1774631480
OL,3,CWoman who had upto 300 seizures before
OL,4,Cbreakfast hails life-changing treatment
OL,6,F"I'm trying to make a coffee or hold a
OL,7,Fconversation, and it's just like not
OL,8,Fhappening because you're not there,
OL,9,Fand you're in and out, and in between
OL,10,Fthe seizures, you're trying to
OL,11,Frecover, but it's so hard."
OL,13,FHolly had what's known as Absence
OL,14,FEpilepsy for almost 20 years.
OL,16,FShe was diagnosed aged 10, but within
OL,17,Fthe last few years, it worsened and
OL,18,FHolly was hospitalised because of the
OL,19,Fseizures and felt there was no hope
OL,20,Fleft.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G3/9
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,415,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41404
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F414A1774631480
OL,3,CWoman who had upto 300 seizures before
OL,4,Cbreakfast hails life-changing treatment
OL,6,FShe tried several medications, none of
OL,7,Fwhich worked, and she suffered badly
OL,8,Fwith side effects, especially relating
OL,9,Fto mental health.
OL,11,FBut in the past year, Holly's had a
OL,12,Fvagus nerve stimulation implant fitted
OL,13,F- a small device near her collarbone
OL,14,Fthat sends pulses to a major nerve to
OL,15,Fhelp prevent seizures.
OL,17,FShe says it's transformed her life,
OL,18,Fsometimes leaving her seizure-free.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G4/9
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,415,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41405
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F414A1774631480
OL,3,CWoman who had upto 300 seizures before
OL,4,Cbreakfast hails life-changing treatment
OL,6,F"Having that dramatic change, and
OL,7,Fhaving the ability to ride my bike to
OL,8,Fwork and sort of just wake up in the
OL,9,Fmorning and not have those seizures is
OL,10,Fjust such a dramatic change," Holly
OL,11,Fsaid.
OL,13,F"I feel alive again.
OL,15,F"I'm so thankful.
OL,17,F"It's a bit odd, because I'm sort of
OL,18,Ffinding out who I am.
OL,20,F"I still love running, and I still
OL,21,Flove the gym as I did before."
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G5/9
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,415,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41406
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F414A1774631480
OL,3,CWoman who had upto 300 seizures before
OL,4,Cbreakfast hails life-changing treatment
OL,6,FHolly ran the Brighton Marathon,
OL,7,Fshowing that with the right treatment
OL,8,Fand determination, epilepsy doesn't
OL,9,Fneed to define you.
OL,11,FMore than 600,000 people in the UK are
OL,12,Fliving with epilepsy, one of the
OL,13,Fcountry's most common neurological
OL,14,Fconditions.
OL,16,FExperts say while anti-seizure
OL,17,Fmedications help many patients control
OL,18,Ftheir condition, about one third still
OL,19,Fexperience seizures even after trying
OL,20,Fmultiple drugs.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G6/9
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,415,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41407
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F414A1774631480
OL,3,CWoman who had upto 300 seizures before
OL,4,Cbreakfast hails life-changing treatment
OL,6,FSpecialists say greater awareness is
OL,7,Fneeded around the range of treatment
OL,8,Foptions available when medication
OL,9,Falone isn't effective.
OL,11,FPaediatric Consultant & Epilepsy
OL,12,FExpert, Dr Amit Bali said: "There are
OL,13,Ftreatments for it.
OL,15,F"The whole point of the treatments is
OL,16,Fpatients can live fulfilling lives and
OL,17,Fachieve all the things that they are
OL,18,Finterested in and want to do.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G7/9
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,415,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41408
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F414A1774631480
OL,3,CWoman who had upto 300 seizures before
OL,4,Cbreakfast hails life-changing treatment
OL,6,F"I think that positive spin on it is
OL,7,Fwhat we try and emphasise with the
OL,8,Fpeople we look after.
OL,10,F"Rather than the opposite which is my
OL,11,Ffear - that's where the stigma comes
OL,12,Ffrom, the lack of understanding and
OL,13,Fthe lack of awareness."
OL,15,FIf you or someone you know is in need
OL,16,Fof support you can contact the
OL,17,Ffollowing organisations:
OL,19,FEpilepsy Society
OL,21,FEpilepsy Action
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G8/9
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
